description: Dropped support for Node.js 12. Developers should use Node.js 14 or higher when deploying the Admin SDK.

Upgraded TypeScript to v4.6.4: firebase-admin version 11.0.0 uses @google-cloud/storage version 6.0.0 which depends on typescript v4.6.4 hence if you want to upgrade to firebase version 11.x you will also need at least typescript v.4.6.4.
